title: Earth Science Papaya Glycolic Gentle Skin Peel, 4 Ounce Tubes
description: This herbal peel yields instant and dramatic results without the use of chemicals. Unlike Retin-A and chemical peels, this peel is gentle on the skin. Papaya Enzymes loosen dead skin cells; Bentonite Clay, Potato Starch, and Kelp Extract pull impurities from the pores (eliminating blackheads); Almond Meal completes the treatment by delicately polishing your skin. Complexion is immediately radiant. Gentle enough for all skin types and perfect for those typically too sensitive for Alpha Hydroxy Acids.

title: Blinc Kiss Me Mascara, Dark Brown
description: Stop painting your lashes, tube them. Kiss Me is the original mascara invented to form tiny water resistant tubes around your lashes rather than painting them like conventional mascaras. Once applied, the tubes bind to your lashes and cannot run, smudge, clump, or flake, even if you cry or rub your eyes. Kiss Me mascara will add both volume and length to give you a radiant natural look that lasts all day. Only when you are ready for removal, the tubes will effortlessly slide off your lashes into your hand without the use of a harsh makeup remover. Made in Japan
